            <p>Similarly, a subjunctive is required
                after the use of the verb '<em>willian - to wish</em>', as this is expressing a desire. For example,
                examine the sentence, '<em>Alexander wolde þæt his mærþa wæren maran þonne Ercoles - Alexander wished
                    that his fame might be
                    greater than Hercules'</em>'.
            </p>
